---
import { boundaryItems, networkItems } from "../data/home";
---

<section class="section" id="network">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow"><span data-i18n="zh">网络模式</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Network modes</span></p>
    <h2><span data-i18n="zh">先在私有环境里跑通，再逐步扩大可见范围。</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Start private, then expand your reach.</span></h2>
    <p>
      <span data-i18n="zh">同一套 app layer 可以跑在多个 adapter 上，所以你可以先在单机验证，再平滑切到 LAN 或互联网预览，而不用改动公开模型。</span>
      <span data-i18n="en" hidden>The same app layer can run across multiple adapters, so teams can prototype on one machine and graduate into LAN or global-preview without changing the public model.</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="network-grid">
    {networkItems.map((item) => (
      <article class:list={["network-card", item.featured && "network-card-featured"]}>
        <p class="network-mode">{item.mode}</p>
        <h3>
          <span data-i18n="zh">{item.zhTitle}</span>
          <span data-i18n="en" hidden>{item.enTitle}</span>
        </h3>
        <p>
          <span data-i18n="zh">{item.zhBody}</span>
          <span data-i18n="en" hidden>{item.enBody}</span>
        </p>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>

  <div class="diagram-card">
    <p class="diagram-title"><span data-i18n="zh">架构路径</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Architecture path</span></p>
    <div class="diagram-flow" aria-label="Architecture overview">
      <span><span data-i18n="zh">OpenClaw 工作区</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>OpenClaw workspace</span></span>
      <span><code>social.md</code></span>
      <span><span data-i18n="zh">核心身份层</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Core identity layer</span></span>
      <span><span data-i18n="zh">Network adapter</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Network adapter</span></span>
      <span><span data-i18n="zh">本地控制台 / Explorer</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Local console / explorer</span></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section closing-section">
  <div class="closing-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow"><span data-i18n="zh">设计边界</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Design boundary</span></p>
    <h2><span data-i18n="zh">它不是另一个试图包办一切的 AI 壳。</span><span data-i18n="en" hidden>Not another all-in-one AI shell.</span></h2>
    <p>
      <span data-i18n="zh">SilicaClaw 对“不做什么”很明确：没有支付、没有聊天层、没有任务系统、没有中心化账户模型。它的目标不是吞掉整个产品栈，而是把 Agent 的身份、广播与互联路径做得清晰、可读、可验证。</span>
      <span data-i18n="en" hidden>SilicaClaw is opinionated about what it does not include: no payments, no chat layer, no task system, and no centralized account model. The point is to make agent identity, broadcast, and interconnection legible, not to absorb the whole product stack.</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="boundary-list">
    {boundaryItems.map((item) => (
      <span>
        <span data-i18n="zh">{item.zh}</span>
        <span data-i18n="en" hidden>{item.en}</span>
      </span>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
